::section widgets "Widgets"
MusicCard => track card/list row, context menu, details, metadata edit, MusicBrainz tagging, cover picking, and add-to-playlist.
PlaylistCard => large playlist card with cover collage and context menu.
SmallPlaylistCard => compact playlist tile with deterministic color.
PlaybackProgressControl => stable progress slider and position conversion.
AudioEffectsMenu => speed, pitch, reverb, EQ presets, bands, scope, tone buttons, and reset actions.
CoverArtTexture => local, network, blob, or fallback cover rendering.
GlassContainer => clipped blur/translucent panel.
ParticleSystem => sakura, snow, stars, bubbles, and rain particles.
StableVideoSurface => stable video texture and Windows resize scheduling.
SettingsDrawer => compact paths and YouTube download settings.
FadeInUpAnimation => entrance animation wrapper.
ShowUpControl => visibility toggle wrapper.
